{"tid":1919144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"據悉今晚再多2名埃及團團友確診武肺 今日單日或增加5宗確診","createTime":"2020-03-10T14:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T17:41:48.000Z","uid":212626,"like":78,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"2b6575e4fe6579cb3f743d477a15e263b0a90fda","tid":1919144,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:52:06.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎在本港沒有停止迹象，<span style=\"color: red;\">據悉，再多2名參與新華旅遊埃及10天團的團友，確診感染武漢肺炎，即「埃及旅行團」8人群組中，已有3人確診感染，有指兩人正留醫屯門醫院。連同衞生署下午公佈的3宗武漢肺炎確診個案，今日單日已增加5宗確診</span>。確診者中有2人涉及印度旅行團，是曾參加印度旅行團後到加拿大溫哥華並在當地確診男子的女兒及工人；而該確診男子目前正在溫哥華的醫院深切治療部留醫。此外，由郵輪「鑽石公主號」返港的港人當中，其中一人被日本當局檢出呈陽性並於之後康復，不過今日懷疑「復發」，再次被驗出唾液含病毒，衞生防護中心指，該病人有免疫系統相關的長期病患，屬於「免疫力超低」的病人，返港後再驗出陽性是預料之內。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200310/75MJOR6VTGVE56I2T6POBTWIJA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200310%2F75MJOR6VTGVE56I2T6POBTWIJA%2F&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=a9c66235\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200310%2F75MJOR6VTGVE56I2T6POBTWIJA%2F&h=423738b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200310/75MJOR6VTGVE56I2T6POBTWIJA/</a>"},{"pid":"18dd6f7423696f491080793bd582b53d14df83a3","tid":1919144,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2d29475c990813c1a3a7046622247719dd1c49","tid":1919144,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c14bc5cd0acd9296352de049a721f06964c605","tid":1919144,"uid":158613,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:55:00.000Z","